author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | Angela Scanlon's Close Encounters
text: The lovely Angela Scanlon returns to our screens for a brand new series tonight which sees her spending 24 hours with a variety of famous faces. She kicks things off tonight by hanging out with Irish pro-wrestling star Sheamus, whose real name is in fact Stephen Farrelly. Hailing from Cabra on the northside of Dublin, Sheamus/Stephen has been part of the World Wrestling Entertainment circuit for the past six years, getting to grips with its grueling schedule as well as stardom. Angela finds out a bit more about the man behind the muscle as she goes backstage to follow the build-up to a so-called 'grudge match' between Sheamus and his current feuding partner, Randy Orton.
